OL,6,FA former detective who had a
OL,7,Frelationship with a sex offence victim
OL,8,Fwhose case he investigated has been
OL,9,Fjailed.
OL,11,FWasim Bashir, 55, was found guilty of
OL,12,Fmisconduct in a public office for
OL,13,Fhaving a sexual relationship with the
OL,14,Fwoman while working in the Kirklees
OL,15,Fsafeguarding team with West Yorkshire
OL,16,FPolice.
OL,18,FSheffield Crown Court heard the 22-
OL,19,Fyear-old woman met Bashir after
OL,20,Freporting a sexual assault to police
OL,21,Fin 2020.
