OL,6,FShe said she met Bashir and a female
OL,7,Fofficer to give a statement, but he
OL,8,Fgot in touch with her a few days later
OL,9,Fenquiring about her wellbeing.
OL,11,FThe woman, who had mental health
OL,12,Fissues, said she was grateful for his
OL,13,Fconcern and agreed to meet him for a
OL,14,Fcoffee.
OL,16,FThey started a sexual relationship
OL,17,Fwhich stopped when she started seeing
OL,18,Fsomeone else.
