OL,6,FThe woman said they stayed in touch
OL,7,Funtil she became aware that he had
OL,8,Fposted photographs of the two of them
OL,9,Fon an adult "swingers" website
OL,10,Fpresenting them as a couple.
OL,12,FShe said she complained to Bashir, who
OL,13,Fapologised and promised to delete it.
OL,15,FJurors heard the woman decided to
OL,16,Freport the relationship to police at
OL,17,Fthe end of 2021.
