OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement read
OL,7,Fduring Friday's sentencing hearing,
OL,8,Fthe woman said the man she was
OL,9,F"supposed to trust" manipulated her
OL,10,Fand used her for sexual gratification.
OL,12,FThe statement read: "I should have
OL,13,Fbeen able to trust him due to the
OL,14,Fposition he held within the police."
OL,16,FIn mitigation, Jason Pitter KC said
OL,17,Fthe breakdown of Bashir's marriage in
OL,18,F2017 had had a profound impact on him.
