OL,6,FBashir, who has since retired from the
OL,7,Fforce, was cleared of another charge
OL,8,Fof misconduct in a public office
OL,9,Falleging he contacted two other women
OL,10,Finappropriately.
OL,12,FJailing Bashir for two years and three
OL,13,Fmonths, judge Charles Thomas said:
OL,14,F"Your behaviour towards (the
OL,15,Fcomplainant) was a gross breach of
OL,16,Ftrust...You prioritised your own
OL,17,Fsexual gratification."
